{"word":"παρατίθημι","slug":"παρατίθημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παρατίϑημι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, τίϑημι</el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘place <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> beside’, <b>set before:</b> a parable <b><a href='B:470 13:24'>Mt 13:24</a>, <a href='B:470 13:31'>31</a>;</b> food <b><a href='B:480 6:41'>Mk 6:41</a>; <a href='B:480 8:6'>8:6f</a>; <a href='B:490 11:6'>Lk 11:6</a>; <a href='B:510 16:34'>Ac 16:34</a></b> (by metonymy); <b><a href='B:530 10:27'>1 Cor 10:27</a>.</b> Mid., <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on submitting details <b>demonstrate, point out <a href='B:510 17:3'>Ac 17:3</a>; <a href='B:510 28:23'>28:23</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘assign for security or safekeeping’, <b>entrust, commend</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> indicating personal interest in a matter <b><a href='B:490 12:48'>Lk 12:48</a>; <a href='B:490 23:46'>23:46</a>; <a href='B:510 14:23'>Ac 14:23</a>; <a href='B:510 20:32'>20:32</a>; <a href='B:610 1:18'>1 Ti 1:18</a>; <a href='B:620 2:2'>2 Ti 2:2</a>; <a href='B:670 4:19'>1 Pt 4:19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παρατήρησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παρατυγχάνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}